			<h2 class="heading-bg clearfix mar_20_t mar_20_b"><span>Featured</span></h2>
			<ul class="features hor3 clearfix">
			<li>
				<a href="http://mb.cpf.ca/about-us/what-is-cpf/"><img width="278" height="106" src="http://mb.cpf.ca/wp-content/blogs.dir/1/files/mission-278x106.jpg" class="attachment-feature-home-3 size-feature-home-3 wp-post-image" alt="mission" /></a>
				<h3>What is CPF?</h3>
				
				<p class="no-subtitle">Canadian Parents for French (CPF) is a national volunteer organization of adults who recognize the value of learning French and actively promote opportunities for young Canadians to learn and use French.</p>
				<p><a href="http://mb.cpf.ca/about-us/what-is-cpf/" class="more">More <span>&rsaquo;</span></a></p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a href="http://mb.cpf.ca/about-us/branches/starting-a-chapter/"><img width="275" height="106" src="http://mb.cpf.ca/wp-content/blogs.dir/1/files/chaapter-275x106.jpg" class="attachment-feature-home-3 size-feature-home-3 wp-post-image" alt="chaapter" /></a>
				<h3>Starting a Chapter</h3>
				<h4>You can help bring CPF activities to your community!</h4>
				<p>Do you live in a community that is not currently being served by a CPF chapter? It could be up to you to start one! </p>
				<p><a href="http://mb.cpf.ca/about-us/branches/starting-a-chapter/" class="more">More <span>&rsaquo;</span></a></p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a href="http://mb.cpf.ca/resources/for-parents/french-for-life/"><img width="278" height="106" src="http://mb.cpf.ca/wp-content/blogs.dir/1/files/FFL-screen-mockup-278x106.jpg" class="attachment-feature-home-3 size-feature-home-3 wp-post-image" alt="FFL-screen-mockup" /></a>
				<h3>French for Life</h3>
				<h4>Say oui to opportunity</h4>
				<p>An amazing website about learning French in Manitoba.</p>
				<p><a href="http://mb.cpf.ca/resources/for-parents/french-for-life/" class="more">More <span>&rsaquo;</span></a></p>
			</li>						
			</ul>					<div class="pad_20_t"></div>
					
